'''三(2-吡啶基)膦'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>15</sub>H<sub>12</sub>N<sub>3</sub>P，它是三吡啶基膦的[[同分异构体|同分异构体]]之一。它可由[[2-溴吡啶|2-溴吡啶]]和红[[磷|磷]]在碱性条件下反应制得。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=European Journal of Organic Chemistry|volume=2014|issue=3|language=en|date=2014-01|pages=639–643|doi=10.1002/ejoc.201301453|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/ejoc.201301453|title=Reaction of Tri(2-pyridyl)phosphine with Electron-Deficient Alkynes in Water: Stereoselective Synthesis of Functionalized Pyridylvinylphosphine Oxides: Stereoselective Synthesis of Pyridylvinylphosphine Oxides|accessdate=2020-09-20|author=Svetlana N. Arbuzova, Nina K. Gusarova, Tatyana E. Glotova, Igor A. Ushakov, Svetlana I. Verkhoturova, Anastasiya O. Korocheva, Boris A. Trofimov}}</ref>它和灰[[硒|硒]]回流，可以得到三(2-吡啶基)硒化膦<!-- CAS号：26832-47-3 -->。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Phosphorus, Sulfur, and Silicon and the Related Elements|volume=193|issue=5|language=en|issn=1042-6507|date=2018-05-04|pages=300–305|doi=10.1080/10426507.2017.1417295|url=https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1080/10426507.2017.1417295|title=Synthesis, crystal structures and magnetic properties of two iron (II) tris(pyridyl)phosphine selenides complexes|accessdate=2020-09-20|author=Xuecheng Hu, Tingquan Sun, Chunyang Zheng}}</ref>

